commentPostTextItems.html: India win by six wickets with 6.1 overs remaining
Tendulkar takes the batting honours with a patient and determined unbeaten knoc
Cuffy  bowled yet another inspiring spell 10-3-20-1, the big wicket of Sourav G
Ridley Jacobs had yet another memorable match, top-scoring with an unbeaten 53
Another convincing win for India, clearly the better side amongst the three par
kindly send us your views/comments/opinions to comms@cricinfo.com
We will be back with you from Bulawayo with the live coverage of match # 5, Zim
The game starts at 0700 Hrs GMT. So long

stories.title: India complete third successive triumph in Coca-Cola Cup
stories.summary:
India continued their run of success in the triangular tournament,
with a six-wicket victory over West Indies, who found themselves two
wickets down after three overs on a flat but sluggish pitch, and were
never in the game thereafter

stories.title: Indian bowlers restrict West Indies
stories.summary:
India made West Indies resemble a schoolboy team in restricting them
to 169 for seven in 50 overs in a triangular one-day series match in
Bulawayo today

stories.title: 4th Match, India v West Indies, Coca Cola Cup, Statistical Highlights
stories.summary: It was the 1731st ODI in cricket history
